    "description": "云霄一刻是一款反约会的视觉小说和甜甜圈烹饪模拟游戏的混合。<br><br>在这款游戏中，你在好爆工作，这是一家特殊的咖啡馆，提供改变情绪的甜甜圈，帮助人们逃离日常生活的折磨。作为一名情绪甜品师，找出哪种情绪最适合帮助陷入困境的顾客是工作的一部分。从让他们高兴起来的口味，到激起苦乐参半的回忆的口味，完美的甜甜圈取决于你的选择。<br><br>如果这还不够，你的前任们回来了——作为你无法拒绝的顾客——他们的到来让事情变得更复杂。遗憾的是，“结束关系”并不是菜单上提供的情绪之一，所以这需要你使用真诚的力量来驾驭复杂的情绪，或许，还可以用一两个甜甜圈。<br><br>如果你喜欢甜甜圈、戏剧性故事和揉面团，那么准备好迎接云霄一刻吧！🍩🌿<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/e9082d07283d1940a5a1974ca3039b1e.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/e9082d07283d1940a5a1974ca3039b1e.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/e9082d07283d1940a5a1974ca3039b1e.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩甜蜜的心理疗法</strong><br>作为一名情绪甜品师，找出哪种情绪最适合帮助陷入困境的顾客是工作的一部分！你的武器库中有各种各样的口味，每一种都对应一种特定的情感——勇气、真诚、愉快、耐心等等。你的顾客的反应取决于你为他们提供的心情，所以要小心！这不仅仅是提供甜甜圈，你也在提供人生建议。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/3443d474b2c303cd01d8c2910421924b.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/3443d474b2c303cd01d8c2910421924b.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/3443d474b2c303cd01d8c2910421924b.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩成为城里最好的甜甜圈店</strong><br>管理咖啡厅，从零开始准备和设计甜甜圈，为顾客提供正确的订单，让顾客满意，收集小费，解锁新食材和发掘新食谱！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/07550b06d46bb0c00f4b3e0bfc9cf64f.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/07550b06d46bb0c00f4b3e0bfc9cf64f.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/07550b06d46bb0c00f4b3e0bfc9cf64f.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩从五段关系中走出来</strong><br>准备好迎接大戏吧，因为你的前任们回来了——作为你无法拒绝的顾客——他们的到来让事情变得更复杂。遗憾的是，“结束关系”并不是菜单上提供的情绪之一，所以这需要你使用真诚的力量来驾驭复杂的情绪，或许，还可以用一两个甜甜圈。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/def8dbb19f3d2c41e921e4ece7d2ada2.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/def8dbb19f3d2c41e921e4ece7d2ada2.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/def8dbb19f3d2c41e921e4ece7d2ada2.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩英语配音</strong><br>专业的英语配音演员将为角色们带来生命！每个角色都会有配音，除了玩家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/4ba7c314604057c1c9d0cb9b1909f1db.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/4ba7c314604057c1c9d0cb9b1909f1db.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/4ba7c314604057c1c9d0cb9b1909f1db.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩选择很重要&amp;多重结局</strong><br>你提供的甜甜圈和你做出的选择最终会影响你与顾客的关系。你是会迷失在暂时的兴奋中，把事情弄得一团糟；还是找到结束关系的方法？他们会记住你对他们说过的话，所以在做出选择之前要三思！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/abaebd9805c2afa162e1a5e3733fa4f3.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/abaebd9805c2afa162e1a5e3733fa4f3.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/abaebd9805c2afa162e1a5e3733fa4f3.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩别样的角色</strong><br>除了你的前任们，圣马索城到处都是滑稽的人物——比如穿着小鸡装的女孩，或者拿着刀的坏鸭子。去了解他们，为他们提供最喜欢的甜甜圈，并找出他们的动力来源。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/514f2164a4f0fde9c5eecda3cb412d93.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/514f2164a4f0fde9c5eecda3cb412d93.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/514f2164a4f0fde9c5eecda3cb412d93.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩可自定义的主角</strong><br>选择一张让很多人心碎的脸来获得沉浸式体验。玩家可以选择男性或女性角色，并可以自由地自定义外观，如肤色，发型等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/643d79579d96692fdc4d167a8a5b34a5.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/643d79579d96692fdc4d167a8a5b34a5.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/643d79579d96692fdc4d167a8a5b34a5.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩动态漫画风格的视觉效果</strong><br>动态漫画风格的面板和充满活力的CG让你的故事变得栩栩如生！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/02078962a2ca8ef9838af307d3411d6f.poster.avif?t=1764057915\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/02078962a2ca8ef9838af307d3411d6f.webm?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251220/extras/02078962a2ca8ef9838af307d3411d6f.mp4?t=1764057915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🍩原声音乐</strong><br>原声音乐将让你沉浸式体验烹饪时间！",
